    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/624b57d0b1fae00b04228d6c0bf42881.avif?t=1697314869\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br>Fall onto a planet where only water will survive. Explore, complete missions from the outback. Or even loot. In the world of Fish Bone, you will find different technologies, magic and eras on each island. play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/9cfd18f6a41a4f71a9447c864adc45bb.poster.avif?t=1697314869\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/9cfd18f6a41a4f71a9447c864adc45bb.webm?t=1697314869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/9cfd18f6a41a4f71a9447c864adc45bb.mp4?t=1697314869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>survival<br>-Explore resources It's the main factor you need to look for.<br>- Craft weapons, tools contribute to the number of more resource acquisitions.<br>-Build buildings such as walls to protect monsters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/a94a3a76a7e6d3e852cffe7e2efa7080.poster.avif?t=1697314869\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/a94a3a76a7e6d3e852cffe7e2efa7080.webm?t=1697314869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/a94a3a76a7e6d3e852cffe7e2efa7080.mp4?t=1697314869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build a ship and decorate it<br>-artillery<br>- Armor<br>- large drill<br><br>survey<br>-Explore a world full of water You must have a vehicle<br>- Various treasures are waiting for you to find.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/9cc57b690d01f1ba3ce5dd48df2c9a71.avif?t=1697314869\" width=686 height=344 /></span><br>Play as a bounty hunter to receive large amounts of prize money<br><br>Build a workshop to produce tools and materials.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/1a39653abf0bfe71e3eaac0c93ecbb7d.poster.avif?t=1697314869\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/1a39653abf0bfe71e3eaac0c93ecbb7d.webm?t=1697314869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/1a39653abf0bfe71e3eaac0c93ecbb7d.mp4?t=1697314869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/f634f0b68272542601de457dbc6443b5.poster.avif?t=1697314869\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/f634f0b68272542601de457dbc6443b5.webm?t=1697314869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/f634f0b68272542601de457dbc6443b5.mp4?t=1697314869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207220/extras/39dc41d116e9fddd334498f91d799bbe.poster.avif?t=1697314869\" width=600 height=300 ><source src